_sText:
Hi this is a map i made because my clan wanted a battle field.. If you have played on my prior map i like to make fields. This map has no advantage to either team. Think of going to a paint-ball field and this is what its like at night.. 


Ps: This map is best played with 10 to 30 players 

My name is John and i enjoy making simple maps email me at knight@blaze.clanservers.com
